snippet.title: BEAST QUEST – Official Video Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on an epic action-adventure to save the Kingdom of Avantia from ruin. https://www.maximumgames.com/beast-quest/

Based on the best-selling fantasy novels, Beast Quest is coming to consoles for the first time ever, with a rich storyline, action-packed combat, and a world filled with adventure and treasure!
